trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of string elements separated by commas.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling strengen elementer atskilt med semikolon.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan arves.

trans-unit.source: This class represents a string collection that is serialized as a comma-delimited list of string elements.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen representerer en streng samling serialisert som en kommadelt liste over streng elementer.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Adds a string to the comma-delimited collection.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en streng i kommadelt-samlingen.

trans-unit.source: This method causes the <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A> property to be set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden får den <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A>egenskapen settes til `true`.</xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A>

trans-unit.source: A string value.
trans-unit.target: En strengverdi.

trans-unit.source: Adds all the strings in a string array to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Legger til alle strenger i en strengmatrise i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The `range` parameter must be an array rather than a comma-delimited string.
trans-unit.target: Den `range` parameteren må være en matrise i stedet for en kommadelt streng.

trans-unit.source: An array of strings to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av strenger for å legge til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Clears the collection.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner samlingen.

trans-unit.source: This method causes the <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A> property to be set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden får den <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A>egenskapen settes til `true`.</xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates a copy of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Oppretter en kopi av samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A copy of the <xref href="System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En kopi av det <xref href="System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Adds a string element to the collection at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Legger til en streng-element i samlingen i den angitte indeksen.

trans-unit.source: This method causes the <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A> property to be set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden får den <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A>egenskapen settes til `true`.</xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A>

trans-unit.source: The index in the collection at which the new element will be added.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen i samlingen som det nye elementet blir lagt til.

trans-unit.source: The value of the new element to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Verdien for det nye elementet skal legge til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that specifies whether the collection has been modified.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om samlingen har blitt endret.

trans-unit.source: The IsModified property is `true` after the <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Clear%2A>, <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Insert%2A>, or <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Remove%2A> method has been called.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen IsModified `true` når den <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Add%2A>, <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Clear%2A>, <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Insert%2A>, eller <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Remove%2A>har blitt kalt.</xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Remove%2A> </xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Insert%2A> </xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Clear%2A> </xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Add%2A>

trans-unit.source: Also, the IsModified property is `true` after the <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Item%2A> property is used to modify an element of the string collection.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen IsModified er også `true` når den <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Item%2A>egenskapen brukes til å endre et element i samlingen streng.</xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.Item%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref href="System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection"></xref> has been modified; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den <xref href="System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection"> </xref> har blitt endret; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the collection object is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den er skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: This property returns `true` if the collection is marked as read-only.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen returnerer `true` hvis samlingen er merket som skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: This is useful for protecting the element at run time, as opposed to design time.
trans-unit.target: Dette er nyttig for å beskytte elementet ved kjøretid, i motsetning til utformingen.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement.IsReadOnly%2A> method on the <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement?displayProperty=fullName> class.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement.IsReadOnly%2A>-metoden på <xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement?displayProperty=fullName>klasse.</xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Configuration.ConfigurationElement.IsReadOnly%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the specified string element in the <xref href="System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection"></xref> is read-only; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis det angitte strengen elementet i den <xref href="System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection"> </xref> er skrivebeskyttet; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a string element in the collection based on the index.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir et streng-element i samlingen basert på indeksen.

trans-unit.source: This property allows a string in the collection to be set or retrieved based on its index in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan en streng i samlingen til å angi eller hente basert på indeksen i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: This property also causes the <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A> property to be set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen gjør også at den <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A>egenskapen settes til `true`.</xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A>

trans-unit.source: The index of the string element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for streng-element i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: A string element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: En streng-element i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Removes a string element from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner en streng-elementet fra samlingen.

trans-unit.source: This method causes the <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A> property to be set to `true`.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden får den <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A>egenskapen settes til `true`.</xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsModified%2A>

trans-unit.source: The string to remove.
trans-unit.target: Strengen som skal fjerne.

trans-unit.source: Sets the collection object to read-only.
trans-unit.target: Angir collection-objektet til skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether the <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection> collection can be modified, call the <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Å finne ut om den <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection>samlingen kan endres, kan du kontakte den <xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsReadOnly%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection.IsReadOnly%2A> </xref:System.Configuration.CommaDelimitedStringCollection>

trans-unit.source: Returns a string representation of the object.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en strengrepresentasjon av objektet.

trans-unit.source: A string representation of the object.
trans-unit.target: En strengrepresentasjon av objektet.
